The Cathedral is the heart of the Order’s power. From here the Grand Magister commands his fanatical forces and enjoys total dominion over the surrounding lands. Usually one might only hear whispers in the hallowed corridors but now they are filled with the sounds of blades being drawn and armored boots hitting stone. Dim moonlight pours in through the high windows as an unearthly battlecry bellows forth from the decaying throats of your minions.
